Cannoli are sweet Italian pastries, also known as cream horns. 
Ingredients
    • Fried pastry dough in the shape of a tube 
    • 2 tablespoons ricotta cheese 
    • 1 tablespoon whipped cream 
    • 1 tablespoon sugar 
    • 1 tablespoon chocolate chips 
    • ½ tablespoon icing
Procedure
    1. Fry dough into shells 
    2. Mix the ingredients except the shells. 
    3. Stuff shells with the mixture. 
    4. Cool in the fridge 
    5. Serve.
